title: 822. Takeaways from The Match & Drafting Top 10 Edge Rushers
itunes:title: 822. Takeaways from The Match & Drafting Top 10 Edge Rushers
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys give their takeaways from The Match, the golf event with the team of Aaron Rodgers and Tom Brady vs. Josh Allen and Patrick Mahomes. Then, the guys do a draft where they each pick their top 5 edge rushers.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
